{"tid":2321031,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好鍾意食魚腐 所以 自製魚腐⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-12-11T08:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T20:49:17.000Z","uid":375024,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"280f909ad5ec816e1c0dcaa7f4d6f2e383c69e47","tid":2321031,"uid":375024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"平時買魚腐得20蚊四両<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n決定買條魚自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一步梗係起肉先<br />\n太腥 當然要戴住口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKreHSY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKreHSY.png&h=031cb07e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4FQONjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4FQONjG.jpg&h=72a43d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶得搵部機 人手剁算 正常係要起魚皮 不了 好煩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g2ra0Fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg2ra0Fk.png&h=b7c7d380&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WA81nTL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWA81nTL.png&h=6f9db288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將啲魚肉打到起膠 落蛋落水 <br />\n拎去炸炸炸 搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgCJBeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgCJBeC.png&h=6ea3d957&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wNhFGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wNhFGn.png&h=e7601f46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9abK8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9abK8c.png&h=af850305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後啲骨唔好嘥咗佢！ 滾返個靚魚湯先<br />\n完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次整 冇想像中咁脹卜卜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nG4gbO1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnG4gbO1.png&h=5c053424&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Du6Y9AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDu6Y9AM.png&h=c09d1274&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb2c04f07bdae791c92ac0ad8dd703d3c0a3c1c2","tid":2321031,"uid":297182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"好似好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76697b615c4facbc1bbd2c08b477fd1fbbdc315","tid":2321031,"uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"好核突同殘忍<br />\n碎屍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9144ef3b651a14de80a5a072f209c84799f2eb9","tid":2321031,"uid":155295,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"a76697b615c4facbc1bbd2c08b477fd1fbbdc315","tid":2321031,"uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"好核突同殘忍<br />\n碎屍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"師兄冇食過蒸肉餅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38cdbebbe8a7d6a04a5cd64d6748de2cc5d4721","tid":2321031,"uid":5728,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a76697b615c4facbc1bbd2c08b477fd1fbbdc315","tid":2321031,"uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"好核突同殘忍<br />\n碎屍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"好奇你平時飲食習慣係點"},{"pid":"ea16ece3b9a3fd0362d62601ed665cb5fed86f2e","tid":2321031,"uid":380166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"原來就係你 <br />\n頭先喺單位一直聽到剁肉聲<br />\n